* Reverse sort order
* `upload` torrent files
* `upload`ed files should support moving to tags (e.g. `ruget Something.torrent -m Downloads` - or via `-t Downloads`)
* `remove` items
* Filter to download files above or below a certain size (e.g. `-s '>1gb' -s '<2gb'`)
* Auto assume wrapping globs around terms (e.g. 'ruget foo' -> 'ruget *foo*')
* Add `move: 'Seed'` to `.ruget.json` options to assume `-m Seed` on successful downloads
* Add prompt when cancelling a download: `Cancelled. (r)etry, (m)ark as done, (n)ext`
* Screenshots in doc
